notes.text:

- CVE-2023-3966: Fixed invalid memory access in Geneve with HW offload (bsc#1219465).

notes.text: A flaw was found in Open vSwitch where multiple versions are vulnerable to crafted Geneve packets, which may result in a denial of service and invalid memory accesses. Triggering this issue requires that hardware offloading via the netlink path is enabled.
